Necross/ Splattercannon/ Hellplague:
 
Hellplague bows and leaves the chamber.  Necross turns and faces the image of Unicron.
"Almighty Unicron.  May we continue?"
 
Splattercannon watches Hellplague leave with a wary look.  Her attitude bewilders the Minion, and he decided to rmain on guard, Malice may try something.
